OL,5, For the past two years, Nikhil Arora   
OL,6, has been working hard to cut his       
OL,7, organic gardening company's carbon     
OL,8, footprint, taking small steps, like    
OL,9, shifting away from plastic packaging,  
OL,10, to make his business, Back to the      
OL,11, Roots, the most environmentally        
OL,12, efficient it has ever been.            
OL,14,FThe California-based company is small, 
OL,15,Femploying just 21 people, but it       
OL,16,Fexpects to make roughly $100m (#84m) in
OL,17,Fsales this year. Mr Arora says the     
OL,18,Fmoves it has made are critical to the  
OL,19,Ffight against climate change.          
